    "text": "Thanks."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.72,
    "endTime": 13.24,
    "text": "She's nasty as you are."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.98,
    "endTime": 15.66,
    "text": "You know..."
  },
  {
