    "text": "Princess!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.56,
    "endTime": 32.56,
    "text": "Wait, wait - What are you doing?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.649,
    "endTime": 42.46,
    "text": "Be still, mon cherie, for I am your savior, and I am rescuing you from this green...  beast."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.46,
    "endTime": 44.751,
    "text": "Hey, that's my princess."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.751,
    "endTime": 45.75,
    "text": "Go find your own."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.14,
    "endTime": 50.86,
    "text": "Please, monster, can't you see I'm a little busy here?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.36,
    "endTime": 54.66,
    "text": "Look pal, I don't know who you think you are."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.66,
    "endTime": 56.76,
    "text": "Oh! Of course, how rude, alala."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.94,
    "endTime": 59.101,
    "text": "Please let me introduce myself."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.101,
    "endTime": 61.28,
    "text": "Oh, merry men!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.62,
    "endTime": 70.64,
    "text": "I steal from the rich and give to the needy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.74,
    "endTime": 71.33999999999999,
    "text": "He takes a wee percentage."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.34,
    "endTime": 72.62,
    "text": "But I'm not greedy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.62,
    "endTime": 74.80000000000001,
    "text": "I rescue pretty damsels, man, I'm good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.8,
    "endTime": 75.56,
    "text": "What a guy!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.56,
    "endTime": 76.0,
    "text": "Ha ha!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.0,
    "endTime": 76.84,
    "text": "Monsieur Hood."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.84,
    "endTime": 77.34,
    "text": "Break it down."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.66,
    "endTime": 83.86,
    "text": "I like an honest fight and a saucy little maid."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.86,
    "endTime": 85.62,
    "text": "What he's basically saying is he likes to get..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.62,
    "endTime": 86.10000000000001,
    "text": "Paid!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.1,
    "endTime": 87.08,
    "text": "So!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.08,
    "endTime": 88.89999999999999,
    "text": "When an ogre in the bush grabs a lady by the tush."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.9,
    "endTime": 91.30000000000001,
    "text": "That's bad, that's bad, that's bad, that's bad."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.3,
    "endTime": 94.0,
    "text": "When a beauty's with a beast it makes me awfully mad."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.0,
    "endTime": 95.7,
    "text": "He's mad, he's really, really mad."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.7,
    "endTime": 97.7,
    "text": "Now I'll take my blade and ram it through your heart."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.7,
